* Install Ubuntu LTS 14.04 in virtualbox
* Once the installation is finished, install the Vbox companion ttool (Device, insert guest additions), and then reboot
* Install the latest jdk in /opt/
* Install the preinstall version of TTool for Linux, reconfigure ttool.exe to point to the right installation of the jdk
* Install other necessary tools : sudo apt-get install g++ gtkwave graphviz

That's all folks!